id catches here in the US while your fishing for ""real"" fish. Its a kids fish that you can catch here in the US without even trying.So really just have no desire to fish ""ponds"" for carp and bream. When the game gets completed I will give it another review. But I have my doubts that any American fish will be represented well because of the disconnect they seem to have to our fishing world(US). I don't think there is an American among them and fishing in England is apparently vastly different than it is here."
